<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>DevOOPS</title>
        <meta name="description" content="description">
        <meta name="author" content="DevOOPS">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.1.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
		<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Righteous' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
        <link href="http://www.brimes.com.br/assets/devoops.css?body=1" rel="stylesheet">
    </head>
    <body>
        <!--Start Header-->
        <header class="navbar">
            <div class="container-fluid expanded-panel">
                <div class="row">
                    <div id="logo" class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2">
                        <a href="www.brimes.com.br">Brimes</a>
                    </div>
                    <div id="top-panel" class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-4">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-8 top-panel-right">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div id="main" class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div id="content" class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12">
                    <br/>
                    <div class="col-xs-1 col-sm-2 col-lg-2"></div>
                    <div class="col-xs-10 col-sm-8 well">
                    <h4>Seja bem vindo.</h4>
                    <br/>
                    Você solicitou um cadastro no site www.brimes.com.br. Para confirmar o cadastro clique no botão abaixo para habilitar o seu acesso.<br/>
                    <br/>
                    <% link_reg = "#{CONFIG["app_host"]}usuarios/confirmacao_cadastro?email=#{@data['email']}&token=#{@data['token']}"%>
                    <%= link_to "Confirmar cadastro", link_reg, :class => "btn btn-lg btn-success"%>
                    <br/><br/>
                    Caso não tenha solicitado o cadastro desconsidere esse email.
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-1 col-sm-2 col-lg-2"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
